# Keep the working tree byte-identical on every platform.
#
# Windows checkouts default to core.autocrlf=true, which rewrites text files to
# CRLF on checkout. That would mean the YAML fixtures, catalog packs and skill
# files a Windows contributor reads are not the bytes CI reads — and risqlet
# writes LF explicitly (newline="\n"), so a CRLF working tree would also show
# spurious diffs the moment the CLI rewrites a register.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Never translate binary-ish assets.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.whl binary
